    <section class="hero">
      <span class="hero-badge">Self-Hosted &middot; Open Source</span>
      <h1>
        Manage your <span class="accent">media libraries</span> with confidence
      </h1>
      <p>
        A self-hosted webapp for Plex, Jellyfin, and Emby. Browse and filter
        your libraries, automate media lifecycle with rules, manage streams, and
        integrate with the *arr stack.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/docs/getting-started/installation/" class="btn btn-primary">
          Get Started
        </a>
